  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个车辆状态流转图。核心状态有三个：静止、行驶和碰撞。起点和终点都用终止符表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。起点指向静止状态，那静止状态能直接回到终止吗？比如车辆报废或者任务结束的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，静止可以回到终止。另外静止和行驶之间要双向转换，表示启动和停车。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "[*]",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这些画出来：起点到静止，静止到终点，静止和行驶互相切换。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还差一个关键分支：行驶状态可能发生意外，要有一个碰撞状态。碰撞之后车辆就彻底结束了，直接指向终止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，碰撞只能从行驶进入，不能从静止直接进入对吧？而且碰撞是单向到终止，不能恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，这样逻辑就完整了。你检查一下所有状态都有入边和出边吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "检查完毕：起点和终点形成闭环，静止和行驶双向连通，碰撞作为异常终点。图已经画好了。",
